typedef pair<int, int> pii;
typedef long long LL;
#define MOD 1000000007
#define INF 1000000000

pii arr[300][300];
int maxRow[300];
int maxCol[300];

LL fpow(LL A, LL B, LL mod) {
	LL ans = 1;
	while (B > 0) {
		if (B%2 == 1)
			ans = (ans*A)%mod;
		A = (A*A)%mod;
		B >>= 1;
	}
	return ans;
}

int main() {
	int T;
	scanf("%d", &T);
	for (int t = 0; t < T; t++) {
		int N, M;
		scanf("%d %d", &N, &M);
		LL A1, A2, B1, B2, mod;
		scanf("%lld %lld %lld %lld %lld", &A1, &A2, &B1, &B2, &mod);
		for (LL i = 0; i < N; i++) {
			for (LL j = 0; j < M; j++) {
				arr[i][j].first = (int)fpow((A1*(i+1)+A2*(j+1))%mod, mod-2, mod);
				arr[i][j].second = (int)fpow((B2*(i+1)+B1*(j+1))%mod, mod-2, mod);
			}
		}
		for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
			int _max = 0;
			for (int j = 0; j < M; j++)
				_max = max(_max, arr[i][j].second);
			maxRow[i] = _max;
		}
		for (int j = 0; j < M; j++) {
			int _max = 0;
			for (int i = 0; i < N; i++)
				_max = max(_max, arr[i][j].first);
			maxCol[j] = _max;
		}
		int done = 0;
		for (int i = 0; i < N; i++) {
			for (int j = 0; j < M; j++) {
				if (arr[i][j].first == maxCol[j] && arr[i][j].second == maxRow[i]) {
					done = 1;
					printf("%d %d\n", i+1, j+1);
					break;
				}
			}
			if (done)
				break;
		}
		if (!done)
			printf("-1\n");
	}
	return 0;
}
